headline.print_headline: Ex-Survivor Lead Singer Died of Stroke, Drugs
headline.main: Ex-Survivor Lead Singer Died of Stroke, Drugs

lead_paragraph: An autopsy report shows that Jimi Jamison, the lead singer on Survivor hits such as "Burning Heart" and "Is This Love," died of a stroke with methamphetamine intoxication.
